- Yeah.

06:49.928 --> 06:51.906
Hey! So Emmett...

06:51.907 --> 06:53.938
- totally on board.
- Sweet!

06:53.939 --> 06:56.843
Toby's gonna get some extras from Buckner,

06:56.844 --> 07:00.633
Wilke's going to play a guard
and John got all these costumes

07:00.634 --> 07:02.806
