14:20.903 --> 14:22.243
That very comment tells me how

14:22.244 --> 14:24.208
little you can be trusted
with this equipment.

14:24.209 --> 14:27.193
- C'mon, Randall.
- Look, evenf I could bend the rules,

14:27.194 --> 14:29.703
