I just don't have anything to say.

18:36.929 --> 18:38.337
Kathryn, come on.

18:38.848 --> 18:42.000
I did not mean to tell her
about the miscarriage, okay?

18:43.000 --> 18:45.158
Kathryn, all right, it just came out.

18:45.402 --> 18:46.690
Over drinks at her hotel?

18:46.691 --> 18:48.443
