31:08.585 --> 31:09.631
Can you help carry some

31:09.632 --> 31:11.587
of that lighting equipment
out to the pool?

31:11.621 --> 31:14.623
Totally. I was just gonna grab
some zombie fingers first.

31:17.594 --> 31:19.661
You hooked up with Emmett?

31:20.098 --> 31:22.497
What? No.

31:24.571 --> 31:26.768
I heard you had somebody in
your room at the tournament,

31:26.802 --> 31:28.736
which I figured was just a rumor.

31:28.771 --> 31:30.771
And then I read your texts.

31:30.806 --> 31:32.773
Look, it was a complete mistake.

31:33.855 --> 31:36.678
You gotta understand that
I had just lost the game, and

31:37.927 --> 31:40.615
Toby had bailed on me and I was drunk.

31:40.649 --> 31:43.485
- That's your excuse?
- No.

31:44.010 --> 31:46.856
I mean... look, I'm...
I'm trying to explain to you

31:46.890 --> 31:49.626
that it was really messed up,
but I just don't think

31:49.660 --> 31:51.895
that everything should be
blown up out of proportion

31:51.929 --> 31:54.732
over something that happened
once that meant nothing.

31:54.766 --> 31:57.917
Toby is my best friend.
And what about Bay?

31:57.917 --> 32:01.435
Look, if I could go back in
time and undo things, I would.

32:02.808 --> 32:04.604
Please, I am asking you to

32:04.604 --> 32:06.811
just let this one die
for everybody's sake.

32:08.680 --> 32:09.701
Please.

32:11.770 --> 32:15.026
"Dawn of the deaf," scene four, take five.

32:15.026 --> 32:15.852
Marking.

32:19.490 --> 32:20.890
We set? Ready?

32:21.722 --> 32:23.627
And action.

32:25.497 --> 32:27.698
He's coming. Oh god.

32:28.919 --> 32:30.968
You have to shoot him. It's the only way.

32:41.949 --> 32:44.617
Oh no. No no no no!

32:44.651 --> 32:45.918
No no no. No.

32:46.920 --> 32:48.587
Okay, get Bay's close-up.

32:52.625 --> 32:54.759
And Emmett's.

32:56.762 --> 32:58.763
And cut!

32:58.797 --> 33:00.731
That's a wrap.

33:00.765 --> 33:03.600
Great job, everybody!
You should be so proud.

33:04.769 --> 33:08.222
That was amazing, even if I did kill you.

33:08.222 --> 33:10.775
Very moving. Very moving!

33:11.810 --> 33:13.878
Hey, you guys, look!

33:13.912 --> 33:16.681
- Oh wow.
- Look at the cake. What a great cake.

33:16.715 --> 33:19.381
What a cool cake.

33:20.315 --> 33:22.241
